-- AcidPit Trajectory Redirect v3
-- Synced with Trajectory Finder API + visible AcidRedirect arc.
-- Features:
-- - Returns Controller
-- - Cleans old controller
-- - WaitForChild timeouts
-- - Uses external PredictPlayerLanding API if passed from loader
-- - Falls back to internal predictor if no external API is provided
-- - Draws visible trajectory arc when velocity/prediction activates
-- - Clears arc when idle/stopped/destroyed

